These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Birthday: august, january, march, november
Job: photographer, dressmaker, writer, nurse
1. Birthday:august is on the right of Job:writer##1
2. Job:nurse is on the far left##1
3. Job:writer is between Job:dressmaker and Birthday:january##2
4. Birthday:november is on the far left##1
5. Birthday:march is between Birthday:january and Birthday:august##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | november         | january   | march | august       |
| Job      | nurse | photographer | writer   | dressmaker |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
City: colone, hannover, london, paris
Flower: amaryllis, tulip, lily, balloon-flower
1. Flower:balloon-flower is between City:london and Flower:tulip##2
2. City:paris is on the far right##1
3. Flower:lily is on the right of Flower:amaryllis##1
4. City:colone is on the left of Flower:amaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| City         | hannover | colone | london | paris |
| Flower   | tulip    | balloon-flower   | amaryllis | lily       |

