.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Hobby: cooking, drawing, sudoku, writing
Movie-Genre: action, musical, superhero, comedy
1. Movie-Genre:superhero is on the right of Hobby:writing##1
2. Movie-Genre:superhero is between Movie-Genre:musical and Hobby:drawing##2
3. Movie-Genre:musical is on the far left##1
4. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left of Hobby:sudoku##1
5. Hobby:drawing == Movie-Genre:comedy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby          | writing    | cooking | drawing   | sudoku  |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | superhero   | comedy | action |

